      "step_index": 4,
      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "- **Structural alerts**\n  - **Aryl\u2013(basic amine)\u2013aryl** motif is a well-known hERG risk pattern.\n  - **Piperazine + aromatic systems** is a common hERG-associated combination (though not as stereotyped as \u201cpiperidine + aromatic,\u201d it\u2019s in the same risk family).",
